bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid=
; background-color: #ccc;">dissented from the proposed rules</a> on the gro=
unds that if you tell people too much about how funds vote they will be hij=
acked by activists:</p><blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">While fund =
shareholders may not be interested in this information, activists of every =
stripe can use the fact that funds have to publish their votes to increase =
their leverage through intimidation and negative publicity. =C2=A0Thus thes=
e stakeholders shape how proxy votes are cast.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:=
 16px 0;">A fund shareholder looking to earn a return so she can retire may=
