scope=3D"itemscope" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !importa=
nt; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-s=
tyle: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> talked the other day</a> about a sha=
reholder proposal at Fox Corp. that explicitly argued that the proposal mig=
ht be bad for Fox=E2=80=99s bottom line,=C2=A0but will good for all the oth=
er companies that Fox shareholders also own.=C2=A0That is the way of the=C2=
=A0future.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Oh by the way the rules also req=
