olor: #ccc;">current rules</a> insiders generally have to disclose their st=
ock trading shortly=C2=A0<em>after=C2=A0</em>they do it, and those disclosu=
res seem to have <em>long</em>-term predictive power. From the <a href=3D"h=
ttps://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/25195151.265551/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3=
